
Task
Powers of number 2
Get an array of powers of 2: [1, 2, 4, 8, 16 ...]
 
Write a function called powersOfTwo that takes n as an argument and returns an array of powers of 2 (powers from 0 to n).
Example:
• the powersOfTwo (2) function must return [1, 2, 4];
• the powersOfTwo (4) function must return [1, 2, 4, 8, 16]

Solution
function powersOfTwo (n) {
let arr = [];
for (let i = 0; i <= n; i ++) {
arr.push (Math.pow (2, (i)));
}
return arr;
}
